text: El Chirú is a corregimiento in Antón District, Coclé Province, Panama. It has a land area of and had a population of 3,623 as of 2010, giving it a population density of . Its population as of 1990 was 2,518; its population as of 2000 was 2,830. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Coclé Province
